		<span class="csEEC52858">CHAPTER 18B. HIGHER EDUCATION.</span></h1>
	<h2 class="csCA36641A">
		<span class="cs317696C1">ARTICLE 14. MISCELLANEOUS.</span></h2>
	<h4 class="csCA36641A">
		<span class="cs6D9F0C8B">&sect;18B-14-1. Select committee on outcomes-based funding models in higher education.</span></h4>
	<p class="cs45E53620"><span class="csE736517A">[Repealed.]</span></p><h4 class="csCA36641A">
